<div class="bibitem" id="bibitem-1">1. &quot;On the feasibility of an alliance with 'reality-benders' in the cause of science&quot;; address by Dr Robert Scranton to Her Majesty's Fellowship for the Study of Curiosities and Phantasmagoria; 12 October 1889.</div>
<div class="bibitem" id="bibitem-2">2. Brumell, J (1978). &quot;A History of the Fourth Occult War&quot;; <em>Prometheus Publications</em>.</div>
